Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to talk to you about tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to go see the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't go outside, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Onii-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just how cute you are in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:52.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How to put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You kind of look like Muramasa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.51,0:00:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How cute you are in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And how you kind of look like\NMuramasa-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,See, she usually wears kimonos and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And she's really pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, I mean, you're just as much...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, she confessed her love to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How'd you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can tell as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's just like you, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She confessed in the same way you did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But I don't know your reply to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I turned her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I said I was in love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.77,0:01:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right. Is that so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I asked\Nbecause I was interested or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you feel about her right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course, I like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Huh? You said you turned her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did turn her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But she said my novels were\N{\i1}the most interesting in the world{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was the first time someone told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.59,0:02:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I've gotten to like her a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- How much?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How much do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,W-Well, about second in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is first?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who? Say it. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ni-Nii-san, why do you say stuff like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.59,0:02:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just because I'm turned down doesn't mean\Nmy love is going to suddenly change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But that's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Or rather, Sagiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you wearing that yukata?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be sleeping over\Nat the editorial office tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, work for the upcoming book.\NIt's crunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll leave your food in the fridge,\Nso make sure to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And, if you need anything, call me right away.\NI'll come back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know! You're too overprotective!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you still angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not a kid. I'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Take care, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And now, I will commence home security!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have secured the safety\Nof my home tod—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-san! Are you not home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}It's him. How dare he surprise me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Hurry up and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:32.97,3rd,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\pos(645.717,153.444)}Sorry we missed you!\NTo: Sagiri Izumi\NWe attempted to deliver,\Nbut resident was not home.\NFrom: Amu Amu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.10,0:06:37.85,DefaultRightH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a5\pos(153.7,408.444)}Figures from:\NLegend of the Illusionary Demon Sword
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san, hurry home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm so looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I wonder if that guy\Nwill be there again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sagiri is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:07:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}I'm here in Chiba City right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Today in Chiba City,\Nthe Civilian Fireworks Festival will be held.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Many people are here to celebrate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, I'd like to interview people on the street.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm here with my family to see the fireworks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope I can come here\Nwith a boyfriend next year!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you her older sister?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Y-Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have a cute younger sister!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}I'm currently looking\Nfor a handsome boyfriend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Come now, be quiet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not jealous or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Those sisters really do get along.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Now, back to you in the studio!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.91,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can use this place as much as you want.\NGood luck with turning it into a long novel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When you're done,\Nplease hand it over to the part-timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, do your best! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're going home?\NNo check-throughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll do it tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}How cute you are in that yukata...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You kind of look like Muramasa-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's it, but that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong, Nii-san?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.44,0:08:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you eat your meal?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You called just to ask me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you I'd be all right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:08:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nothing. Don't stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yup. Good luck with your work, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Such a weird Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Sorry we missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I forgot to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.82,0:09:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you thinking about\Nwith a serious look on your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think Sagiri wants to go\Nto the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was thinking if I could do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.13,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Siscon.\N- Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, what's with that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.63,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm cute, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did you go to supplementary class\Nso you can get enough attendance days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I came over here to flaunt\Nhow lovely I look in my school uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do I look? A lot more charming\Nthan someone like Muramasa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've been working this entire time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I just finished up and heading back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheesh. So that's why\Nyou didn't answer the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh well. I have a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shidou Kunimitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The rookie author who lost against you\Nin the Light-novel Tenkaichi Budoukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A wrap party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.05,0:10:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I got an invite from a Twitter DM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was hoping we can have it at your place,\Nwith me and Eromanga-sensei there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shidou-sensei is okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After all, he missed getting published\Nbecause I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,About that. Apparently, his story\Nis going to be published anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:11:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, they decided to publish\Nup to the "third-place piece" as books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,H-Hold on a second! I thought they didn't have\Nthe luxury of increasing publishing slots?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There were more slots?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"We increased it because I did my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Winning or losing shouldn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In the end, you have to publish\Ninteresting works!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And such. I mean, that's something\Nyour editor would totally say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}But their release dates are going to be\Npretty far off in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}You wouldn't have been able\Nto continue being an author like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}If that's the case, it's not like Shidou-sensei\Nhas a grudge against me or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Problems all solved?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, there's still one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seeing Muramasa-senpai would be, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You dumped her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see, so she might feel awkward\Nand may not want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what you're thinking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:12:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How stupid to worry over\Nsomething that may or may not be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.47,0:12:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One chat settles it for sure,\Nso why don't you talk to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're really amazing at stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,More like, what's wrong?\NYou're rather honest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Have you fallen in love with Elf-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be great\Nif you were my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't need a little brother like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.55,DefaultC,NTP,0,0,0,,Change your look for the summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.52,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(324.683,335.111)}Are you ready for hot summer dates?\NYou won't be watching\Nthe fireworks alone, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, I'll put her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's from your beloved Izumi-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then I'll just hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Speaking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Muramasa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, that is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why are you speaking politely?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-I mean, this is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was surprised, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I asked for your contact information,\Nand she said you were right next to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you in a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it doesn't matter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, Masamune-kun,\Nyou wanted to speak to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, there's going to be a Light-novel\NTenkaichi Budoukai wrap party at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you'd like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but you probably don't, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't I want to?\NI'll go if I had to risk my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's fine? I mean, the thing with me, um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just because I got turned down doesn't mean\Nmy love for you will change so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You really don't seem to understand me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've only met you three times so far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My regards for the future, kouhai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The pleasure is mine, senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, hello. My name is Shidou Kunimitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is this Izumi Masamune-sensei's residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I'm Izumi Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, just as I thought!\NIt's a pleasure to meet you, Izumi-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, the pleasure's mine.\NNice to meet you, Shidou-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please, sit anywhere you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shidou-sensei, you're the only one here so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll go make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Um...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why don't we drop the "-sensei" bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,As you requested, I've become\Nthe most beautiful girl in a yukata for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Masamune-kun, was this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shidou-kun is here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.24,0:15:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll be right next to Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're being audacious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yama-something-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why do you only vaguely remember my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, Masamune-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you listening!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll take the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D-Don't get so close like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you so slovenly just for Muramasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm way cuter than she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cute, not cute, that doesn't matter\Nwhen you're not dressed like normal—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because a yukata—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.32,0:16:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}A poltergeist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-In any case, Izumi-kun,\Nyou're really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? He's not popular at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Izumi-sensei already\Nhas someone he's in love with, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wouldn't be moonstruck\Nfor anyone else, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your voice was rather soft.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will not be moonstruck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I'm going to get the food ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What kind of a relationship are they in?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Don't you be running away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They have a lot going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A lot going on? But they're both guys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think he completely misunderstands us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Masamune-kun, you made all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}I hope it suits your tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}So tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then, enough with the introductions! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Congrats, Masamune.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}{\i1}Handmade?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come to think, your story\Nfor the competition was about sweets, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've always liked sweets ever since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Someday, I'd like to collaborate\Nwith a food company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dream is to have characters or sweets\Nfrom my stories stocked up in stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My great dream is to write\Nthe ultimate light-novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and conquer the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Before heading out into the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to first defeat Dengeki Bunko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.43,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:26.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Starburst Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.27,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dream is to write\Nthe most interesting novel in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...and to read it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I want to make the new title a smash hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and turn it into anime, and watch it here\Ntogether with my younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.29,0:18:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is our dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a great dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do your best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And lastly, your turn, Eromanga-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My dream is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Izumi-sensei already mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.93,0:19:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have one more, don't you?{\i0}
