Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Muramasa, let's go see fireworks!\N- Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kunimitsu, you're coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Was the wrap party fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was ordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone gathered here in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:54.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Everyone ate the same food,\Nand talked about all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was really fun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,On the other hand, now that everyone left,\Nit's all quiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nii-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Were you lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That phone call the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were acting rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, I might have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know, Sagiri, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm scared of being by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mom... my real mother...\Ngot into an accident while I was home alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She never came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So when I gained a new family, I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lost the will to leave my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You alone being all right can't be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I finally figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What you want is a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I want a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I hadn't thought of you as family,\Nand I don't want to be your younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But, since you're so hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.57,0:22:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll pretend to be your younger sister for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've gotten much further away.
